Step welcome
    Out $name + "您好，请问有什么可以帮您?"
    Default listenAndAct
Step listenAndAct
    Listen 10
    Branch "投诉" complainProc
    Branch "账单" billProc
    Branch "流量" broadBandProc
    Branch "维修" serviceProc
    Branch "人工" artificialProc
    Silence silenceProc
    Default defaultProc
Step complainProc
    Out "请描述您的问题"
    Listen 50
    Out "您的意见是我们改进工作的动力，请问您还有什么补充?"
    Default listenAndAct
Step thanks
    Out "感谢您的来电，再见"
    Exit
Step billProc
    Out "您的本月账单是 " + $amount + " 元"
    Out "请问还有什么可以帮您？"
    Default listenAndAct
Step silenceProc
    Out "听不清，请您大声一点可以吗"
    Listen 10
    Branch "投诉" complainProc
    Branch "账单" billProc
    Branch "流量" broadBandProc
    Branch "维修" serviceProc
    Branch "人工" artificialProc
    Silence noOneProc
    Default defaultProc
Step noOneProc
    Out "对不起，系统检测到您可能已离线，随后将自动退出。"
    Default thanks
Step defaultProc
    Out "不好意思，我不太懂您的意思，您可以尝试以下关键词：投诉、账单、宽带、维修、人工"
    Default listenAndAct
Step broadBandProc
    Out "您的流量剩余 " + $broadBand + " MB"
    Out "请问还有什么可以帮您？"
    Default listenAndAct
Step serviceProc
    Out "请输入您的联系方式，我们稍后将为您安排维修人员"
    Listen 50
    Out "请问还有什么可以帮您？"
    Default listenAndAct
Step artificialProc
    Out "请稍后，正在为您接入人工客服"
    Out "已接入"
    Exit